  "text": "Here we present an example including some typical tasks for the system [CITATION_1] . A planar manipulator with four revolute joints mounted on a flexible base is considered. Each of the five links is 1 meter long with mass 1 kg and an identity inertia matrix. The initial offset of the base from its equilibrium posture (the origin) is ∆x b = (0.01, 0.01, 0, 0, 0, 0) and vibrates according to",
